<view class="catalog-page"><custom-navbar eyebrow="服务地点" title="常见就诊医院"/><view class="catalog-content"><search-bar value="{{query}}" placeholder="搜索医院、区域或科室" bindinput="search" bindclear="clear"/><view class="picker-grid"><picker range="{{districts}}" range-key="name" value="{{districtIndex}}" bindchange="district"><view>{{districts[districtIndex].name}} ›</view></picker><picker range="{{levels}}" range-key="name" value="{{levelIndex}}" bindchange="level"><view>{{levels[levelIndex].name}} ›</view></picker><picker range="{{populars}}" range-key="name" value="{{popularIndex}}" bindchange="popular"><view>{{populars[popularIndex].name}} ›</view></picker></view><view class="scope">目前仅服务上海市范围内医院。如需其他城市服务，请加入候补名单。不申请定位权限，也不展示虚构实时距离。</view><view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="loading">正在加载医院…</view><empty-state wx:elif="{{error}}" title="医院加载失败" button-text="重新加载" bindaction="retry"/><view wx:elif="{{items.length}}"><hospital-card wx:for="{{items}}" wx:key="id" hospital="{{item}}" binddetail="detail" bindfavorite="favorite"/><view wx:if="{{hasMore}}" class="loading">继续上滑加载更多</view></view><empty-state wx:else title="暂无符合条件的医院" description="调整筛选条件试试"/></view><login-sheet visible="{{loginVisible}}" bindclose="closeLogin" bindsuccess="loginSuccess"/></view>
